{"tid":1491414,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聽日就721一個月啦, 一齊做啲野呀!! refresh番香港人金魚記憶呀","createTime":"2019-08-20T12:00:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T14:01:02.000Z","uid":264983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9a96a89a1a49c430542400be297c2c37643fdf2f","tid":1491414,"uid":264983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T12:00:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSor9y P牌仔忍唔住啦,<br />\n碌左幾日, 等到呢刻都唔見人帶頭<br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">明天就一個月啦</span></span><br />\n點解冇Post 叫人做啲野去 Refresh 番?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係咪 818 好成功, High到唔記得 721</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sGaKbZG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsGaKbZG.jpg&h=54e6df28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X1fY0S2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX1fY0S2.jpg&h=bb5bd41b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=16CiwPChpr0&amp;has_verified=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D16CiwPChpr0%26has_verified%3D1&d=TRt9Hu9y5T%2Bqj71zgJeH9vGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=78ceeab3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=16CiwPChpr0&amp;has_verified=1</a><br />\n鏗鏘集：721元朗黑夜<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=px1r6T0z-I0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dpx1r6T0z-I0&d=TRt9Hu9y5T%2Bqj71zgJeH9vGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=f373d0cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=px1r6T0z-I0</a><br />\n【紀錄】元朗暴徒攻擊《立場新聞》女性記者，該記者多處受傷，已送醫<br />\n<br />\n唔該大家做啲野去提番班香港人,<br />\n我冇諗到好提議